data.Name: Destino
data.Bio: There are multiple artists with the name Destino: 1) Destino is a group of electronic music in genres like EUROBEAT, EURO HOUSE, HYPER TECHNO, DISCO. Fujisawa Miya works at compositon and arrangement, having a support from Mr. D at vocals. 2) DESTINO - Colombian D-beat Hardcore Punk 3) A japanese rapper. 4) Destino (sometimes known as Destino 4) are a pop opera/classical group featuring Joey Niceforo, Terance Reddick, Roy Tan and Rosemary Siemens.
